{"tid":1242354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立調查委員會絕對唔同監警會 警察投訴科 得獨調會可查邊個問責官員落指令","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:54:20.000Z","uid":221265,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"513438ebf1cafbc8ef74172b2a92c5278ee65060","tid":1242354,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨立調查委員會絕對唔同監警會 警察投訴科<br />\n獨立調查委員會絕對唔同監警會 警察投訴科<br />\n獨立調查委員會絕對唔同監警會 警察投訴科</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好多人唔知 唔識分 唔知佢唔肯成立'有乜後果<br />\n一定要俾人知<br />\n監警會 警察投訴科level完全唔同<br />\n只能report 個別警察<br />\nreport 唔到高位<br />\n同埋絕對唔係獨立<br />\n投訴成功率1%都無<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n獨立調查委員會先有用，要話俾多啲人知！ </span></span>"},{"pid":"92708a6fff101b49f7b1a6511349680a86d29e70","tid":1242354,"uid":221265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"由法官主理嘅獨委會可查邊個係阿頭<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔同監警會 警察投訴科l"},{"pid":"4bee2c5785b280a00164cee65ae60429762405f9","tid":1242354,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n大家要read between the line<br />\n唔好只係情緒發洩！ <br />\n最緊要係知依家係咩situation<br />\n要爭取乜<br />\n同埋educate啲唔知佢講乜嘅人<br />\n咪一味話佢廢話就算</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6ad6ad3662aa5aeed8765326f9ffbc12758cb92","tid":1242354,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c6ce86adc913f427a434f93d64d0c9a3b439932","tid":1242354,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"係成個社會制度問題<br />\n無徹底改革就無出路<br />\n剩係獨立調查未夠, 成立後亦要改革成個政府體制"},{"pid":"8916eaa43df898d6f792e167e3197442d29ef23f","tid":1242354,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c6ce86adc913f427a434f93d64d0c9a3b439932","